This is the pattern recognition lab. work 5

Input file structure:
+-------------+-----+-------------------------+
| first line  | int | number of distributions |
| second line | int | dimention of X          |
+-------------+-----+-------------------------+
repeat (number of distributions) times:
+-------------+-------------------------------------------------+
| first line  | empty                                           |
| second line | double   | a priori probability of distribution |
| third line  | mXdouble | vector of average values             |
| m lines     | mXdouble | matrix of correlations               |
+-------------+----------+--------------------------------------+
